हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A cleaner girl, sent to retrieve a bracelet from the CEO's room, ends up getting intimate and falling asleep with him while drunk. The insomniac CEO sleeps peacefully for the first time in years and starts searching for her. She hides her identity and joins the company.
